<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Killing Mithaniel Marr flags you for: </strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
- Halls of Honor (the same as killing Aerin'Dar, don't have to kill AD ever again)<br>
- Halls of Honor B (All the Halls of Honor Trials, don't have to do them ever again)<br>
- What you would normally get from killing MM. (Half of a Cipher)<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Killing Terris Thule flags you for: </strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
- Plane of Nightmare B (skips having to do the hedge event ever again).<br>
- What you would normally get from killing TT. (Access to Plane of Torment)<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Killing Bertoxxulous flags you for: </strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
- Crypt of Decay (Don't have to re-do Grummus! just kill Bert!)<br>
- What you would normally get from killing Bert. (Half of a Cipher)<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Killing Saryrn flags you for: </strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
- Plane of Nightmare B (skips having to do the Hedge event ever again!)<br>
- Plane of Torment (Skips having to kill Terris Thule ever again)<br>
- What you would normally get from killing Saryrn. (Half of a Cipher)<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Killing Agnarr flags you for: </strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
- Bastion of Thunder (don't ever have to do Askr's quest again!)<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Killing Vallon Zek and Tallon Zek (need both) flags you for: </strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
- Plane of Tactics (don't have to do behemoth anymore!).<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Killing Rallos Zek flags you for: </strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
- Plane of Tactics (don't ever have to do behemoth again)<br>
- Vallon/Tallon Zek (makes sense since you fight them anyways. Don't have to do them singly anymore)<br>
- What you would normally get from Rallos Zek. (Access to Solusek Ro's Chamber in Sol Ro Tower.  <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>*Elemental flags would require you to have all other flags completed, just as they do now.*</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->)<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Killing Solusek Ro flags you for: </strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
- Halls of Honor (Gives you Aerin'Dar)<br>
- Halls of Honor B (Gives you all the trials)<br>
- Plane of Nightmares B (Gives you the Hedge Event)<br>
- Plane of Torment (Gives you Terris Thule)<br>
- Crypt of Decay (Gives you Grummus)<br>
- Crypt of Decay basement (Gives you Carprin)<br>
- Bastion of Thunder (Gives you Askr's PoStorms Quest)<br>
- Mithaniel Marr (Gives you MM's piece of the Cipher)<br>
- Saryrn (Gives you Saryrn's Piece of the Cipher)<br>
- Bertoxxulous (Gives you Bertoxxulous' piece of the Cipher)<br>
- Karana/Agnarr (Gives you Karana's piece of the Cipher)<br>
- Tower of Solusek Ro (Actually, having all the flags listed above flags you for Sol Ro's Tower, so it's just a matter of getting flags straightened out)<br>
- What you would normally get from killing Sol Ro (flags from all Sol Ro Tower minis, access to the Plane of Fire. Require the RZ/TZ/VZ/PoTactics flags for PoFire too.)<br>
